@node Main "Arroze - Documentation"

                              'Arroze'  1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Arroze' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} based on the popular sliding-tile-
puzzle but with a twist: you have to move or rotate arrows in order
to 'move' an empty space from one part of a board to the other,
which is indicated by a coloured square.

  What complicates the game a little is that every time you move or
rotate an arrow, an other arrow may randomly rotate...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

